<p><B>3D Character Animator</B></p>

<p>We are currently looking for a full time <b>3D Character Animator</b>.</p>

<p>Cryptic Studios is hard at work on City of Heroes <a href="http://www.cityofheroes.com">(www.cityofheroes.com)</a>, the 
massively multiplayer online superhero role playing game.</p>

<p><B>Responsibilities:</B></p>
<UL>
<LI>Provide 3D character animation for the numerous heroes, citizens and villains of Paragon City</LI>
<LI>Adhere to game design and animation guidelines</LI>
<LI>Communicate with Lead Animator and Producer</LI>
<LI>Manage own schedule</LI>
</UL>

<p><B>Requirements:</B>
Candidates must have strong 3D character animation skills and a good knowledge of 3DSMax 3.1 (animation, 
rigging and some modeling and texturing). Experience in the gaming industry a plus, but not necessary. Demo 
reels should include examples of humanoid characters: running, jumping, fighting, hefting and hurling large 
objects and any other kind of superhero activity.  Examples of modeling, texturing and any other creative works 
a plus, but your ability to animate is favored above all.</p>

<p>We offer a competitive salary, equity, and full benefits including health, dental, vision, and 401(k) - as well 
as a fun, flexible, informal workplace.</p>

<p>We are currently only interviewing candidates who can legally work in the United States, and who are willing 
to relocate to San Jose, CA.</p>

<p>If you're looking for a place to shine and believe that you have what it takes to contribute to great games, 
apply now!</p>
	
